[0m[49m[39m  34, 484[0m:[39m[49m ## Summary
[0m[49m[38;5;9m- 35     [0m:[38;5;9m[49m <!-- What works, what fails, patterns observed. Be specific. -->
[0m[49m[39m  36, 485[0m:[39m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     486[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **What works**: The eval harness ran successfully across all 90 tasks with concurrency=5. The LLM (Sonnet 4.5) responds and generates code. The agent framework (ReAct loop) executes. Many tasks pass their "no unintended side effects" tests (the 1-2 passes per task are typically vacuous — e.g., "no reviews removed" passes when nothing happened at all).
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     487[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     488[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **What fails**: All 90 tasks fail (0% accuracy). No task is fully completed.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     489[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     490[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **Failure patterns (3 root causes)**:
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     491[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     492[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 1. **Authentication token not passed to API calls** (affects all app-specific tasks — Spotify, Venmo, Phone, etc.): The agent calls login APIs and gets access tokens, but the system prompt doesn't teach it to pass `access_token` to subsequent API calls. All authenticated endpoints return 401 errors.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     493[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     494[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 2. **API name guessing / wrong API discovery** (affects all tasks): The system prompt references `apis.api_docs.search_apis(query="...")` which doesn't exist. The correct APIs are `apis.api_docs.show_api_descriptions(app_name="...")` and `apis.api_docs.show_api_doc(app_name="...", api_name="...")`. The agent wastes steps guessing API names that don't exist.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     495[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     496[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 3. **Step budget exhaustion** (affects all tasks): With MAX_STEPS=10 and multiple steps wasted on auth errors and API discovery failures, the agent runs out of steps before completing any task. Complex multi-app tasks (Venmo + Splitwise, Spotify + SimpleNote + FileSystem) need significantly more steps.
